data.description: Comfort, convenience, and a great location in this well maintained 4 bed/2.5 bath home facing open green space in desirable Dupont. Covered porch opens to the living room with a gas fireplace. Breakfast bar between kitchen and dining. Pantry opens to a roomy 2 car garage. Bedroom on first floor, plus three bedrooms on upper floor including master w/ ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. An upstairs bonus room can be used for your needs. Private fenced backyard. Close to JBLM.
